the fore-hoofes of a Cow burned, and drunke with Wine, or Broth, or other conuenient
liquor: or the powder of Crystall powdred very finely and drunke with Wine
or some broth: or let them eat of boyled Coleworts seasoned with Pepper: or of the
roots of Rapes boyled with Pepper.
                  To cause Women to loose their Milke,Aboundance of Milke. you must apply vpon the nipples of their
