                        , or all three together, It is true, that it is
much giuen to make obstructions, and it restraineth fluxes as mightily: and this is
the cause why such as haue great loosenesse in their bodies do vse it oftentimes, especially,
if it be parched and boild in cowes milke, wherein many little 
