space of two houres, during which time, you may make cleane her water-pot, changing
their mustard-seed euery eight day, and giuing them of the leaues of beets euery
fourth day, and euery twentieth day of the iuice therof, especially, vnto the spink,
being the most subiect of all others to become blind. And that you may keepe them
without lice, you must change their cage euery twentie daies, as also for another reason,
