                  The way to know many and sundrie maladies which
doe happen vnto birds.
                  
                     IT is apparant, that the diseases of birds are diuers, and the diuersitie
thereof causeth diuers effects, and diuers signes, vvhich lying hidden,
the disease continueth vnknowne, and so there is no administring of any
thing, in as much as it is not knowne, whence it commeth, that they are
in that case, nor what disease it is, nor what medicine or remedie is good or conuenient
